statements: SELECT * FROM car_testing_results;
SELECT prototype_id, test_type, max_speed FROM car_testing_results WHERE test_date = '2023-09-15';
SELECT prototype_id, test_type, acceleration_time, handling_rating FROM car_testing_results WHERE max_speed > 200;
SELECT test_date, test_type, handling_rating FROM car_testing_results ORDER BY test_date DESC;
SELECT prototype_id, test_type, max_speed, acceleration_time, handling_rating FROM car_testing_results WHERE acceleration_time < 5.0;
SELECT prototype_id, test_date, max_speed FROM car_testing_results WHERE max_speed > 200 ORDER BY test_date DESC
SELECT * FROM car_testing_results WHERE test_type = 'Acceleration Test' ORDER BY acceleration_time ASC
SELECT prototype_id, test_type, handling_rating FROM car_testing_results WHERE handling_rating > 4 ORDER BY prototype_id
SELECT test_type, max_speed, acceleration_time FROM car_testing_results WHERE max_speed > 150 AND acceleration_time < 5.0
SELECT * FROM car_testing_results WHERE test_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31'
SELECT * FROM CarPrototypes;
SELECT car_model, test_result FROM CarPrototypes WHERE test_result > 0.5;
SELECT prototype_id, car_model, test_date FROM CarPrototypes ORDER BY test_date DESC;
SELECT car_model, test_result, test_date FROM CarPrototypes WHERE car_model LIKE '%sedan%';
SELECT pm.acceleration, pm.top_speed, pm.handling_rating FROM PerformanceMetrics pm JOIN CarPrototypes cp ON pm.prototype_id = cp.prototype_id WHERE cp.car_model = 'SUV';
SELECT * FROM CarPrototypes WHERE test_result > 8.0;
SELECT car_model, test_date FROM CarPrototypes ORDER BY test_date DESC;
SELECT car_model, acceleration, top_speed FROM CarPrototypes JOIN PerformanceMetrics ON CarPrototypes.prototype_id = PerformanceMetrics.prototype_id WHERE top_speed > 200;
SELECT car_model, test_result FROM CarPrototypes WHERE test_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT car_model, acceleration, handling_rating FROM CarPrototypes JOIN PerformanceMetrics ON CarPrototypes.prototype_id = PerformanceMetrics.prototype_id ORDER BY handling_rating DESC;
SELECT * FROM CarPrototypes;
SELECT prototype_name, testing_result FROM CarPrototypes WHERE testing_date = '2022-01-01';
SELECT engineer_name, specialization FROM TestEngineers ORDER BY engineer_name ASC;
SELECT prototype_name, top_speed, acceleration FROM CarPrototypes INNER JOIN PerformanceMetrics ON CarPrototypes.prototype_id = PerformanceMetrics.prototype_id;
SELECT * FROM PerformanceMetrics WHERE braking_distance > 100.00 ORDER BY braking_distance DESC;
SELECT * FROM CarPrototypes WHERE testing_result = 'Pass';
SELECT prototype_name, testing_result FROM CarPrototypes ORDER BY testing_date DESC;

SELECT CarPrototypes.prototype_name, PerformanceMetrics.top_speed, PerformanceMetrics.acceleration FROM CarPrototypes JOIN PerformanceMetrics ON CarPrototypes.prototype_id = PerformanceMetrics.prototype_id WHERE PerformanceMetrics.top_speed > 200;
SELECT engineer_name, specialization FROM TestEngineers WHERE specialization = 'Electrical';
SELECT prototype_name, testing_date, braking_distance FROM CarPrototypes ORDER BY braking_distance ASC;
SELECT * FROM CarPrototypeTestingResults;
SELECT car_model, top_speed, acceleration_time FROM CarPrototypeTestingResults WHERE top_speed > 200;
SELECT car_model, driver_name, feedback_text FROM PrototypeDriverFeedback ORDER BY rating DESC;
SELECT car_model, engine_type, horsepower, torque FROM PrototypeEngineInfo WHERE horsepower >= 300;
SELECT id, car_model, testing_date FROM PrototypeLocationData WHERE elevation < 500;
SELECT * FROM CarPrototypeTestingResults WHERE top_speed > 200;
SELECT car_model, testing_date FROM CarPrototypeTestingResults WHERE acceleration_time < 5.0 ORDER BY testing_date DESC;
SELECT car_model, engine_type, horsepower FROM PrototypeEngineInfo WHERE horsepower > 300 ORDER BY horsepower DESC;
SELECT * FROM PrototypeDriverFeedback WHERE rating >= 4 AND feedback_text LIKE '%excellent%' ORDER BY driver_name ASC;
SELECT car_model, testing_location, elevation FROM PrototypeLocationData WHERE elevation < 1000 ORDER BY testing_location;
SELECT * FROM car_prototypes;
SELECT manufacturer, model, max_speed FROM car_prototypes ORDER BY manufacturer ASC;
SELECT id, model, testing_date FROM car_prototypes WHERE max_speed > 200;
SELECT test_date, speed_performance, acceleration_performance FROM test_results WHERE speed_performance > 90 ORDER BY test_date DESC;
SELECT name, experience_years, specialization FROM test_engineers WHERE experience_years >= 5;
SELECT * FROM car_prototypes ORDER BY manufacturer, model DESC, testing_date ASC LIMIT 5
SELECT model, MAX(max_speed) AS max_speed FROM car_prototypes GROUP BY model HAVING MAX(max_speed) > 200

SELECT prototype_id, test_date, acceleration_performance FROM test_results JOIN test_observations ON test_results.id = test_observations.result_id WHERE test_observations.observation_text LIKE '%excellent%'
SELECT * FROM prototype_photos WHERE photo_url LIKE '%front%' OR photo_url LIKE '%back%'
SELECT name, specialization FROM test_engineers WHERE experience_years > 5 ORDER BY specialization ASC
